title: Sunny 1 Bed Home, Floor to ceiling windows, Courtyard Views
posting_body: ['Welcome to 923 Folsom', "923 has the amenities you're looking for, with one key difference: You won't have to wait in line to use them.", 'Sophisticated living, refined amenities, and perfectly located.', '923 Folsom Street SoMa apartments offer more than meets the eye.', 'Our boutique community offers urban professionals a place to claim the lifestyle they deserve as they live amidst features and additions that are nothing short of stunning - all in a pet-friendly, stylish environment.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Custom kitchen cabinetry', 'HVAC', 'High-speed Internet', 'Floor to ceiling windows', 'Solar shades', 'Wood-style plank flooring', 'Washers & dryers', 'USB outlets', 'Quartz countertops', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Check out the virtual tour: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
